Test Summary:
Verify visibility of various labels, tabs, buttons and Text fields 
on Login Page
Pre condition: User Should be on Login Page
Execution Steps:
Open any Browser and hit the URL:
http://pintailer.com
Expected Result:
Login Page should be displayed with following Buttons:
1.Login (Button)
2.Try Free (Button)
3.Menu Bar (Button)
4.Product (Button)
5.Pricing (Button)
6.Knowledge Base (Button)
7.Support (Button)
8.Login (Label)
9.Username and Password free text field
10.Change Password

Test Summary: Verify succussfull login with valid credentials
Pre condition: User Should be on Login Page
Execution Steps:
1.Enter valid username and password
2.Click on Login
Expected Result:
User should be succussfully login and redirect 
to Profile Section

Pre condition: User Should be login in Application
Execution Steps:
1. Click on Menu Bar Button
2.Then click on logout button
Expected Result: Logout confirmation box should be displayed with 'OK' and 'Cancel' button on it

Test Summary: Verify logout functionality with Cancel button of Confirmation Box
Pre condition: User Should be login in Application
Execution Steps:
1. Click on Menu Bar Button
2.Then click on logout button
3. Click on Cancel button on Confirmation box
Expected Result: Application should not be logout and user remains on User Profile Page

Test Summary: Verify logout functionality with OK button of Confirmation Box
Pre condition: User Should be login in Application
Execution Steps:
1. Click on Menu Bar Button
2.Then click on logout button
3. Click on OK button on Confirmation box
Expected Result: Application should be sucessfully logout and login page should be displayed
